  "rows": [
    {
      "$id": 1,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0010",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Everyone in the unit[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 2,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0020",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "And[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 3,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0030",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You bastard![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 4,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0040",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Why?![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 5,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0050",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Your goal is to escape this\nworld too, isn't it?![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 6,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0060",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Doing something like this\nis completely pointless![ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 7,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0070",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "[ST:wide ]―I wish to know death.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 8,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0080",
      "style": 0,
      "name": ""
    },
    {
      "$id": 9,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0090",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Death, you say?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 10,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0100",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Your intense motivation is the fear of death.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 11,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0110",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That is stronger even than\nyour thirst for life.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 12,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0120",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I wish to understand that.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 13,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0130",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "And for that[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 14,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0140",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Such a massacre...?[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 15,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0150",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You think you'll understand the fear\nof death by killing them yourself?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 16,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0160",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You called your battle with\nus a contest for survival.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 17,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0170",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's a fight to reject death.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 18,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0180",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Did you start this contest\nwithout even understanding that?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 19,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0190",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The defeated in the contest\nshall simply cease to be.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 20,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0200",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That is not death.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 21,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0210",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Naturally, since I possess\nno such concept myself.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 22,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0220",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "To cease to be is[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 23,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0225",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "a pure negation of existence[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 24,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0230",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "But the \"death\" you speak of is\naccompanied by complex emotions.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 25,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0240",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That is what I wish to know.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 26,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0250",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Once you know[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 27,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0260",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "What will you do?[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 28,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0270",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "I have not considered that.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 29,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0280",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "My desires are not rooted\nin emotion, after all.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 30,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0290",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "All actions[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 31,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0300",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "are performed automatically,\ndriven by inevitability.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 32,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0310",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "For something like that[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 33,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0320",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "For something that doesn't\neven count as a reason[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 34,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0330",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 35,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0340",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Enough.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 36,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0350",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Don't try to understand him, Lin.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 37,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0360",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "He's spouting things as if\nthey're self-evident, but[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 38,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0365",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "when it comes down to it, this guy is[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 39,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0370",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "purely and thoroughly evil.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 40,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0380",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "He's our enemy.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 41,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0390",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "But[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 42,
      "label": "xs32120100_JNK0010",
      "style": 4,
      "name": "Warn"
    },
    {
      "$id": 43,
      "label": "xs32120100_SEL0010",
      "style": 3,
      "name": "Caution her not to be misled by his words."
    },
    {
      "$id": 44,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0400",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's right.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 45,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0410",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "The only way to communicate with him[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 46,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0415",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "is through battle.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 47,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0420",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "You're right[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 48,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0430",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Lin.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 49,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0440",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Right now, our mission is to\nprevent any further casualties.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 50,
      "label": "xs32120100_JNK0020",
      "style": 4,
      "name": "Cut to the Chase"
    },
    {
      "$id": 51,
      "label": "xs32120100_SEL0020",
      "style": 3,
      "name": "Tell her that combat is the\nonly means of dialogue."
    },
    {
      "$id": 52,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0450",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "That's exactly right[ST:wide ]―[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 53,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0460",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Lin.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 54,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0470",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "Right now, our mission is to\nprevent any further casualties.[ST:wait ]"
    },
    {
      "$id": 55,
      "label": "xs32120100_MSG0480",
      "style": 0,
      "name": "[ST:wide ]―Understood.[ST:wait ]"
    }
  ]
}